{"tid":139581,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"點先可以脫毒，有1冇巴打教教我","createTime":"2017-03-01T13:57:03.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-01T17:39:53.000Z","uid":78548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"a315b93fdc03a74a4b0dbacdedc24ffad5507ffd","tid":139581,"uid":78548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-01T13:57:03.000Z","msg":"同朋友都可以冇咩野講嘅，莫講話囡囡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a003e59e138f83fb14516728d58e3e01ccb926ba","tid":139581,"uid":45772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-01T14:07:45.000Z","msg":"我係一仔啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"858ced492a9dd0c93fe90e750ea2e31aebc3bc2c","tid":139581,"uid":48426,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-01T15:14:17.000Z","msg":"首先要搵興趣"},{"pid":"413a01e9c28eb451555bb38dbc8fe87cd24557a3","tid":139581,"uid":60635,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-01T15:17:26.000Z","msg":"脫咩毒姐，做佐佐型毒男咪溝死女囉"},{"pid":"53c8c88a33c64c75c3670290e248d238430231b9","tid":139581,"uid":78429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-01T15:24:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>同朋友都可以冇咩野講嘅，莫講話囡囡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你開post應該都預咗我地都無咩野講"},{"pid":"836978a69f263b31c416e5c00fd2d42c7f277894","tid":139581,"uid":78548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-01T17:32:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>脫咩毒姐，做佐佐型毒男咪溝死女囉</blockquote><br />\n有佐佐咁型就等女溝啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa187d063f40c60c34242e10e640d79f244b4c27","tid":139581,"uid":78548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-01T17:33:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>同朋友都可以冇咩野講嘅，莫講話囡囡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你開post應該都預咗我地都無咩野講</blockquote><br />\n唉 自己把口好似唔識開咁"},{"pid":"a10c4dc1e21bbe2902106db529bb7d0d522ce7f1","tid":139581,"uid":78548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-01T17:38:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>首先要搵興趣</blockquote><br />\n搵到都唔多識傾計 好快dead air"},{"pid":"2abc7aefe6b417253629914230fb543037248c66","tid":139581,"uid":35484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-01T17:39:20.000Z","msg":"　　中醫簡單解析打Ｊ危害<br />\n中醫：腎為先天之本，藏五臟六腑之精華。精液係用黎滋潤身體既五臟六腑，你射哂Ｄ精出黎，就會導致五臟功能失調，咁就會出症狀（變樣衰、皮膚差、脫髮 早洩陽痿等）。而且身心其實是一體的，當身體不對了，心理也會出現問題<br />\n《黃帝內經》：「人有五臟化五氣，以生喜怒憂思恐」。情志與五臟的對應關係是：心在志為喜，肝在志為怒，脾在志為思，肺在志為憂，腎在志為恐。腎主恐，所以打Ｊ既你必定有恐懼症，所以你必定會有膽小同社交恐懼症。<br />\n中醫講腎上通於腦，&quot;精生髓，髓生海&quot;，腎精，生骨髓；又長養你的腦海，生腦海。能量本來是供給大腦的，而你卻通過打飛機耗損掉了，結果就是腦力大幅下降，有的人甚至下降到近乎白痴的程度，剛做的事轉身就忘了，怎麼想也想不起來。腦力不行，學業事業都會一塌糊塗"},{"pid":"4d71435b7dca163a9953d5b19c17787df130ed47","tid":139581,"uid":60635,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-01T17:39:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>首先要搵興趣</blockquote><br />\n搵到都唔多識傾計 好快dead air</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔出聲D女會覺得好神秘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}